  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE A NEW CODE SECTION TO BE CODIFIED AS SECTION 75-102-3, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE PROCEDURES FOR THE ADMINISTRATIVE FORFEITURE OF ENDS PRODUCT SEIZED FOR BEING IN VIOLATION OF THE STATE ENDS PRODUCT DIRECTORY LAW; TO CREATE A NEW CODE SECTION TO BE CODIFIED AS SECTION 75-101-7.1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE PROCEDURES FOR THE ADMINISTRATIVE FORFEITURE OF CIGARETTES SEIZED FOR BEING IN VIOLATION OF THE STATE CIGARETTE DIRECTORY LAW; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
